tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'SemanticSearch', detail: 'Search knowledge files for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('SemanticSearch')
const result = await agent(
  `You are executing the semantic-search workflow for a QA question.

Working directory: /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

Execute the file: workflows/semantic-search.md

The input query is:
"入力チェックでエラーがあったときに、エラーメッセージをユーザーに返す方法を教えてほしい（処理方式: ウェブアプリケーション）（目的: 実装したい）"

Follow the semantic-search.md workflow exactly. Read the file first, then execute it step by step.

Return a JSON object with:
{
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "<high|partial>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "selected_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "excluded_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ]
}`,
  {
    label: 'semantic-search',
    phase: 'SemanticSearch',
    schema: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        selected_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
          }
        },
        selected_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
          }
        }
      },
      required: ['selected_sections', 'selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'excluded_sections']
    }
  }
)

return result
